(1656, 10415, '熱血漫畫 VOOMM!!', '', '2008-02-01 00:00:00', 0, 2, 7, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2009-02-18 19:40:14', '2015-02-16 15:47:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1657, 10435, 'Deaf To Our Prayers', '2006年第四張專輯「Deaf To Our Prayers」創作靈感取自19世紀德國浪漫主義詩人"海因里希·海涅"的The Silesian Weavers；音樂上融入大量Death Metal成分將犀利狠重金屬能量大舉提升，並登上年度音樂盛會Wacken Open Air，締造樂團生涯最高峰。首支單曲"Counterweight"秉持一貫不妥協作風，萬噸Metalcore威力瞬間炸裂；"Trespassing The Shores Of Your World"宣洩對獨裁者之不滿怒氣；Melodic Death風格展現"Stay The Course"持續加重分貝音量，譜入Marcus歇斯底里的野獸咆哮；"Of No Avail"輕聲吉他撥弄導引流暢線條，隨後轟出可讓脖子甩到幾乎斷掉的一連串熱血攻勢；而"Dying In Silence"中狂猛疾速直逼暴走程度，帶來最震撼的衝擊效應！', '2006-02-01 00:00:00', 0, 1, 9, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2009-02-19 02:14:23', '2015-02-16 15:47:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1658, 10436, 'Summon In Thunder', '早在Himsa於2003年發行之專輯「Courting Tragedy and Disaster」便受到金屬雜誌Revolver評論"擁有同等極速生猛、技巧旋律的狂熱11首歌"，並被推選為十大"future of metal"樂團之一，而今年的「Summon In Thunder」要拿出樂團真正實力展現出能夠讓凶暴與複雜度共生的與生俱來之才能，並再一次證明先前的預測非曇花一現!! 在悠揚的北歐旋律之後硬擠而上的暴力能量"Reinventing The Noose"，之中旋律與暴力的互相交替證明了Himsa的天生才能，"Haunter"相當標準的新潮流金屬演奏手法－泛音推弦－在這裡聽起來更令人舒服!! 足以把人吹走的優美旋律開場以及流暢的主體"Big Timber"，頗具In Flames後期形態的"Curseworship"，堪稱專輯最具破壞力之歌曲"Summon In Thunder"，在招喚雷電橫掃之後，你還期望什麼活著下來?\r\n\r\n   \r\nCentury Media is extremely proud to welcome HIMSA to its worldwide family. The Seattle-based metal quintet''s ferocious blend of melodic, unrelenting thrash speed mixed with old-school influences resulted in a savage, unique and uncompromising sound that was welcome, refreshing and undeniable. The group continued to carve out their own unique niche in the scene through relentless touring alongside a wide variety of artists from Danzig and Behemoth to As I Lay Dying and Shadows Fall, helping them win over legions of fans worldwide.\r\n\r\nHIMSA further describe their feelings over the new partnership: "We are very excited, thrilled and honored to be asked to join the Century Media army. All of us are huge fans and supporters of the label and have always admired CM''s continuous drive for releasing great and memorable albums throughout the years. The relationships that have grown and prospered between CM and other bands on their roster shows the honesty, loyalty and sincerity they have as a family. We feel it is the best move for us as individuals and as a band. With Sammi Curr (guitars) rejoining HIMSA and writing new material with Kirby Johnson (guitars), our integrity and passion are at an all-time high with this next step. As soon as the new album is recorded, we will be back on the road destroying your towns."\r\n\r\nHIMSA''s debut full-length, Courting Tragedy and Disaster (2003), was hailed by Revolver as "a manic 11-song effort that''s as speedy and raw as it is technical and melodic," earning the band a highlight as one of 10 bands labeled as the "future of metal." However, it was 2006''s Hail Horror that began to show what this band was truly capable of, as they let their brutal catchiness naturally coexist alongside musical complexity. The album, produced by the renowned Tue Maden (The Haunted, Mnemic), perfected the formula that has allowed the band to continue building their own niche in the current metal scene and gaining attention from MTV, FUSE, Revolver, Guitar World, Outburn, Kerrang!, Metal Hammer and countless other outlets.\r\n\r\nIn other news, HIMSA have been added to the Century Family''s Third Annual Christmas Balls show, which takes place Wednesday, Dec. 13th at The Key Club in Hollywood, CA. The event will also feature the L.A.-based quintet In This Moment and will be headlined by Sweden''s Dream Evil, who will be making their American debut and only U.S. appearance of 2006.\r\n\r\nIn 2007, HIMSA are destined to leave their definitive mark on the genre.', '2007-09-18 00:00:00', 0, 1, 9, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2009-02-19 02:23:24', '2015-02-16 15:47:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1659, 10437, 'Stand In Line', '首張專輯"Stand In Line"除了有現任Mr. Big鼓手Pat Torpey (Ex-Ted Nugent)、貝斯手Chuck Wright (Ex-Quiet Riot)、鍵盤手Phil Wolfe的加入，更有Graham Bonnet (Ex-Rainbow，Alcatrazz，MSG) 來擔任主唱一職，而這個黃金組合儼然就是另一支超級樂團Alcatrazz的化身，因為除了主唱Graham雷同之外，吉他手Chris Impellitteri的地位就等於Yngwie Malmsteen與Steve Vai在Alcatrazz一樣，具有吉他英雄主導樂團的精神象徵。\r\n  首曲"Stand in Line"就展現出十足的震撼效果，當教堂的鐘聲響起，一股莊嚴的正氣油然而生，而當Graham寬廣的音域加上Chris的速彈功力相繼出現，馬上令人聯想到Rainbow與Alcatrazz的繼承者非Impellitteri莫屬! 耳熟能響，翻唱自Rainbow的名曲"Since You''ve Been Gone"是專輯的重頭戲之一，\r\n而當年擔任本曲的主唱正是Graham本人，至於Chris的吉他功力則不下於當年的Ritchie Blackmore。旋律優美的世界名曲"Somewhere Over The Rainbow"保有1秒19連音的金屬吉他最速彈世界紀錄，也是全世界吉他player與樂迷爭相收藏的名曲之一!\r\n  此版本還特別加收珍貴的首張EP "Impellitteri"，高音派主唱Rob Rock與Chris的超速彈吉他solo構成了Impellitteri最剽悍的金屬風格，更添加本專輯的收藏價值!\r\n\r\nBand formed by high-speed neo-classical guitarist Chris Impelliteri, whose style is reminiscent of Yngwie Malmsteen. He produced a self-financed album of instrumentals in 1986 and formed his own band in 1987, which consisted of former MSG and Rainbow vocalist Graham Bonnet, keyboardist Phil Wolfe, ex-Quiet Riot bassist Chuck Wright, and ex-Ted Nugent drummer Pat Torpey. This lineup''s only album strongly evoked Rainbow''s style, to the point where Rainbow fans accused Impelliteri of plagiarism. However, the band disintegrated, with Wright joining House of Lords and Torpey going to Mr. Big. Impelliteri played with former Dio keyboardist Claude Schnell and singer Mark Weisz in 1990. — Steve Huey', '1988-02-01 00:00:00', 0, 1, 9, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2009-02-19 02:39:17', '2015-02-16 15:47:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1660, 10438, 'Beautiful Tragedy', 'Los Angeles'' In This Moment had two years in which to hone and perfect their material before getting to work on this, their debut album, but the resulting tunes still impress for containing not a single wasted note or poorly rendered song idea. Beautiful Tragedy''s best single is precisely its title track, whose duality of meaning concurrently defines the band''s intention to mine the rich rewards afforded by the melodic metalcore template. To the fulfillment of that purpose, vocalist and focal point Maria Brink is of course crucial and inseparable; her fierce screeching providing the necessary counterpoint for her own soaring clean singing, which she alternates so effortlessly that she qualifies as the female foil to metalcore''s premiere vocalist Howard Jones. Coincidentally, In This Moment''s musical template bears almost disturbing similarities to that of his band, Killswitch Engage, appropriating their same skill for musical contrast (supple lullabies and sublime dual guitar harmonies offset by complex, but meticulously performed riffs and drum patterns) into remarkably sticky tracks like "Ashes," "Daddy''s Falling Angel," and "Next Life." So sticky, in fact, that one feels compelled to overlook their obvious debt to KSE''s influence when faced with the sheer wealth of instinctive hooks dripping from additional standouts "Prayers," "He Said Eternity," and the string-laden ballad "The Legacy of Odio" (closing acoustic weeper "When the Storm Subsides" is the disc''s only superfluous cut). True, with the exception of Brink''s anomalous female presence, In This Moment tenders nothing truly original to the state of early-2000s metal on Beautiful Tragedy; but in a genre too often marred by the misuse of volume and aggression over substance, sometimes great songs should be cause enough for celebration.', '2008-02-01 00:00:00', 0, 1, 9, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2009-02-19 02:49:35', '2015-02-16 15:47:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1661, 10438, 'The Dream', '自80年代以降，重金屬搖滾樂不斷蓬勃演進，雖然大多都是以男性樂團為主導，不過還是有許多女聲搖滾持續在這樂壇努力耕耘；如早期The Runaways、Heart、Girlschool到現在的Arch Enemy、Within Temptation、Nightwish、The Agonist等等，都是靠著其獨特魅力成功征服全球無數樂迷，替這陽剛味濃厚的男性區塊增添更多色彩。而狂猛氣焰完全不輸Wall of Jaricho的In This Moment更是新世代中最受歡迎的暴女勁旅！\r\n\r\n2005年，來自美國南加州的Maria Brink(主唱)透過朋友認識了對音樂有著同樣抱負的Chris Howorth(吉他)，兩人相談甚歡決定要組起樂團，陸續加入Blake Bunzel(吉他)、Jesse Landry(貝斯)以及Chris老戰友Jeff Fabb(鼓)後In This Moment正式成立。五首自製Demo透過MySpace網友間相互流傳的瘋狂點閱，不但讓樂團名聲迅速水漲船高，同時贏得Century Media青睞簽入旗下。首張專輯「Beautiful Tragedy(2007)」兼具Screamo強烈情緒和Metalcore熱血力道，受到許多年輕一代搖滾酷客的熱烈響應，更被Ozzy Osbourne欽點登上Ozzfest舞台！In This Moment能夠初出茅廬便順利成為所有人的目光焦點除了自身饒富變化與深層意境的詞曲創作外，當然還有美艷女主唱Maria所散發那無比的致命吸引力。\r\n\r\n有了前作的成功起步，In This Moment趕在今年打鐵趁熱推出第二張專輯「The Dream」；不受Metalcore風潮暫緩所影響，這次改走Alternative點綴傳統重金屬/搖滾聲韻路線，帶給樂迷全新的音樂體驗。發行首周更擠進Billboard Top200第70名位置！主打" Forever "有著大量流暢樂句編排，Maria豐富動聽的好歌喉絕對驚艷；"All for You"特別強調雙吉他走位與Solo，突顯正宗Heavy Metal作風；中版曲"Lost At Sea"開頭緩緩鋪陳，後段轉為強而有力的聲調演出；"Her Kiss"帶來久違Nu-Metal聲韻，充滿Otep 、Kittie之澎湃能量；鋼琴聲淡淡彈奏，"Into the Light"是首萬般柔美的抒情小品，叫人為之動容；"The Great Divide"的狂躁嘶吼再度展現憤怒激昂的硬蕊聲線！「The Dream」提供更為耐聽的音場，實為In This Moment集大成於一身的代表作品。\r\n', '2008-09-30 00:00:00', 0, 1, 9, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2009-02-19 03:10:36', '2015-02-16 15:47:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1662, 10441, 'Buried In Oblivion', '入主Century Media的首張專輯「Buried In Oblivion」，由於Rob Doherty與Tim Roth紛紛遭受痛失親人之苦，在歌詞上注入了許多人生黑暗色彩的能量，開頭曲目"Splintered Visions"耳銳的樂迷應該聽的出濃厚前衛變拍以及疾速、拆解複雜的樂器演奏，緊接而來死亡金屬的凶暴與嘹喨清楚的唱腔形成強烈對比!! 開門見山的馬上就讓你感受Into Eternity的獨樹一格!! 頗具Arch Enemy氣味的"Embraced by Desolation"熱血沸騰!! "3 Dimensional Aperture"則是充滿親人逝去的黑暗色彩，"Buried In Oblivion"除了讚嘆Into Eternity優異的編曲技巧之外，空心吉他震盪的極大反差創造迥然迴異的氛圍，反應Into Eternity的陰陽融合更是記上一筆!! 與銜接而上的"Black Sea of Agony"以及再度出現的反差堪稱本專輯之高潮!! 錯過Into Eternity，真的，真的非常可惜!!  ', '2004-02-10 00:00:00', 0, 1, 9, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2009-02-19 03:25:27', '2015-02-16 15:47:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
